<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to Candidate Portal</title>
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0F172A 0%, #1E293B 100%);">
  <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0F172A 0%, #1E293B 100%); padding: 40px 20px;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center">
        <table width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background: #1E293B; border-radius: 20px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.3); box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.2);">
          
          <!-- Header -->
          <tr>
            <td style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #F59E0B 0%, #8B5CF6 50%, #06B6D4 100%); padding: 50px 40px; text-align: center; position: relative;">
              <div style="width: 100px; height: 100px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); border-radius: 50%; margin: 0 auto 20px; backdrop-filter: blur(10px); border: 4px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.4); line-height: 100px; box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);">
                <span style="font-size: 50px;">ðŸŒŸ</span>
              </div>
              <h1 style="color: #ffffff; margin: 0 0 10px; font-size: 36px; font-weight: 800; text-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); letter-spacing: -0.5px;">Welcome, Candidate!</h1>
              <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.95); margin: 0; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600;">Your journey to making an impact starts here</p>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Content -->
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 50px 40px;">
              <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.15) 0%, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.15) 100%); border-left: 4px solid #F59E0B; padding: 25px; margin: 0 0 35px; border-radius: 12px;">
                <p style="color: #F1F5F9; font-size: 18px; margin: 0 0 10px; font-weight: 700;">
                  Hi <span style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, #F59E0B, #8B5CF6); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text;">{{name}}</span>,
                </p>
                <p style="color: #CBD5E1; font-size: 15px; margin: 0; line-height: 1.7;">
                  Congratulations! Your candidate profile has been created. You now have access to your personal candidate portal where you can build your campaign.
                </p>
              </div>

              {{#if eventName}}
              <p style="color: #94A3B8; font-size: 15px; margin: 0 0 35px; text-align: center;">
                You're registered for <strong style="color: #F59E0B; font-size: 18px;">{{eventName}}</strong>
              </p>
              {{/if}}

              <!-- Candidate Code -->
              <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0F172A 0%, #1E293B 100%); border: 2px solid #F59E0B; border-radius: 16px; padding: 30px; margin-bottom: 35px; text-align: center; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.2);">
                <div style="color: #94A3B8; font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-weight: 700;">Your Candidate Code</div>
                <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.2) 0%, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.2) 100%); padding: 20px; border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 15px;">
                  <div style="color: #F59E0B; font-size: 42px; font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: 6px; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; text-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.5);">{{candidateCode}}</div>
                </div>
                <div style="color: #FCD34D; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 15px;">
                  ðŸ”’ <strong>Keep this secure</strong> - You'll need it to access your portal
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Getting Started Steps -->
              <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1) 0%, rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.1) 100%); border-radius: 16px; padding: 35px 30px; margin-bottom: 35px;">
                <h3 style="color: #F1F5F9; font-size: 20px; margin: 0 0 25px; font-weight: 700; text-align: center;">ðŸš€ Quick Start Guide</h3>
                
                <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 18px 0;">
                      <div style="display: flex; align-items: start;">
                        <div style="width: 35px; height: 35px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8B5CF6, #06B6D4); border-radius: 50%; text-align: center; line-height: 35px; font-weight: 800; color: white; font-size: 16px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-right: 15px;">1</div>
                        <div>
                          <p style="color: #F1F5F9; font-size: 15px; margin: 0 0 5px; font-weight: 700;">Log In to Your Portal</p>
                          <p style="color: #94A3B8; font-size: 14px; margin: 0; line-height: 1.6;">Use your candidate code to access your dashboard</p>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 18px 0; border-top: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.2);">
                      <div style="display: flex; align-items: start;">
                        <div style="width: 35px; height: 35px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #06B6D4, #10B981); border-radius: 50%; text-align: center; line-height: 35px; font-weight: 800; color: white; font-size: 16px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-right: 15px;">2</div>
                        <div>
                          <p style="color: #F1F5F9; font-size: 15px; margin: 0 0 5px; font-weight: 700;">Complete Your Profile</p>
                          <p style="color: #94A3B8; font-size: 14px; margin: 0; line-height: 1.6;">Add bio, photos, and all required information</p>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 18px 0; border-top: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.2);">
                      <div style="display: flex; align-items: start;">
                        <div style="width: 35px; height: 35px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10B981, #F59E0B); border-radius: 50%; text-align: center; line-height: 35px; font-weight: 800; color: white; font-size: 16px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-right: 15px;">3</div>
                        <div>
                          <p style="color: #F1F5F9; font-size: 15px; margin: 0 0 5px; font-weight: 700;">Upload Campaign Media</p>
                          <p style="color: #94A3B8; font-size: 14px; margin: 0; line-height: 1.6;">Showcase your best photos and materials</p>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 18px 0; border-top: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.2);">
                      <div style="display: flex; align-items: start;">
                        <div style="width: 35px; height: 35px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #F59E0B, #8B5CF6); border-radius: 50%; text-align: center; line-height: 35px; font-weight: 800; color: white; font-size: 16px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-right: 15px;">4</div>
                        <div>
                          <p style="color: #F1F5F9; font-size: 15px; margin: 0 0 5px; font-weight: 700;">Select Your Categories</p>
                          <p style="color: #94A3B8; font-size: 14px; margin: 0; line-height: 1.6;">Choose which categories you want to contest</p>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 18px 0; border-top: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.2);">
                      <div style="display: flex; align-items: start;">
                        <div style="width: 35px; height: 35px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #06B6D4, #8B5CF6); border-radius: 50%; text-align: center; line-height: 35px; font-weight: 800; color: white; font-size: 16px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-right: 15px;">5</div>
                        <div>
                          <p style="color: #F1F5F9; font-size: 15px; margin: 0 0 5px; font-weight: 700;">Submit for Review</p>
                          <p style="color: #94A3B8; font-size: 14px; margin: 0; line-height: 1.6;">Our team will approve your profile to go live</p>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>
              </div>

              <!-- CTA Button -->
              <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin: 35px 0;">
                <tr>
                  <td align="center">
                    <a href="{{loginUrl}}" style="display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #F59E0B 0%, #8B5CF6 100%); color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; padding: 20px 60px; border-radius: 50px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 17px; box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.4); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;">
                      Access Candidate Portal â†’
                    </a>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <!-- Important Notes -->
              <div style="background: rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.3); padding: 25px; margin-top: 35px; border-radius: 12px;">
                <p style="color: #67E8F9; font-size: 14px; margin: 0 0 15px; font-weight: 700;">ðŸ’¡ Important Reminders</p>
                <ul style="color: #A5F3FC; font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; margin: 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                  <li>Profile must be approved before going live</li>
                  <li>Any updates require re-approval</li>
                  <li>Admin-approved categories cannot be removed</li>
                  <li>Keep your candidate code secure at all times</li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <p style="color: #CBD5E1; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; margin: 40px 0 0;">
                Ready to make an impact?<br>
                <strong style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, #F59E0B, #8B5CF6); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text; font-size: 18px;">The {{appName}} Team</strong>
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Footer -->
          <tr>
            <td style="background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3); padding: 30px 40px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.2);">
              <p style="color: #94A3B8; font-size: 14px; margin: 0 0 10px;">
                Need help? <a href="mailto:support@itfy-evoting.com" style="color: #F59E0B; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;">support@itfy-evoting.com</a>
              </p>
              <p style="color: #64748B; font-size: 12px; margin: 10px 0 0;">
                Â© {{formatDate currentYear}} ITFY E-Voting. Empowering Candidates.
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>

        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>